drm/i915/dsi: Fix chv_exec_gpio disabling the GPIOs it is setting

Set the CHV_GPIO_GPIOEN bit when updating GPIOs from chv_exec_gpio.

Fixes: a0a6d4ffd2ad ("drm/i915/dsi: add support for gpio elements on CHV")
